---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'

const SEO = {
	title: 'Privacy Policy',
	description: 'Read the privacy policy for the Codenetic productivity toolkit and social media posting app.'
}
---

<Layout title={SEO.title} description={SEO.description}>
	<section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12 px-6 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
		<p class="mb-6">This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect the information you provide when using our social media posting app (the "App").</p>

		<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">1. Information We Collect</h2>
		<p class="mb-2"><strong>Account Information:</strong> When you link your social media accounts, we collect your profile ID, page ID, and access tokens required to post content.</p>
		<p class="mb-6"><strong>Content Data:</strong> We store metadata such as captions, media URLs, and scheduled times for posts you create using the App.</p>

		<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
		<ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-6">
			<li>To enable posting content to your connected social media platforms</li>
			<li>To store your preferences and account linkage details</li>
			<li>To send alerts when access tokens are expiring or actions are required</li>
		</ul>

		<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">3. Data Sharing</h2>
		<p class="mb-6">We do not sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties, except:</p>
		<ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-6">
			<li>When required by law</li>
			<li>To the APIs of social media platforms you choose to connect (e.g., Meta/Facebook/Instagram)</li>
		</ul>

		<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">4. Security</h2>
		<p class="mb-6">We use industry-standard security practices, including encryption and access control. However, no digital system can guarantee absolute security.</p>

		<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">5. Your Rights</h2>
		<p class="mb-6">You can request data deletion at any time by contacting us at <a href="mailto:support@codenetic.tech" class="text-blue-400 underline">support@codenetic.tech</a>.</p>

		<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
		<p>We may update this policy periodically. All updates will be posted here with the date of change.</p>
	</section>
</Layout>
